 posthog/test/test_request.py             |  2 +-
 posthog/test/test_utils.py               |  3 +-
 posthog/utils.py                         |  7 ++---
 pyproject.toml                           |  4 ---
 uv.lock                                  | 35 ------------------------
 12 files changed, 19 insertions(+), 71 deletions(-)

